<HEADLINE>
<P>
KING RETURNS TO ROMANIA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
BUCHAREST, Romania 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
King Michael, Romania's former monarch, arrived Tuesday on a surprise visit 
more than 40 years after being forced into abdication and exile by the 
now-ousted Communist leadership. A spokesman said he planned only a short stay 
in his homeland. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wire 
</P>
