<P>
Photo, Steel company owned by John B. Franklin, above, received minority 
contracts, but Franklin said he has not suffered from being Latino. RICK MEYER 
/ Los Angeles Times; Photo, Les Porter; Photo, Walter R. Norwood Los Angeles 
Times; Chart, LOS ANGELES TRANSIT CONTRACTS TO MINORITIES AND WOMEN / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
