<P>
BIDWELL, BENNETT; RETIREMENT; CHRYSLER CORP; EXECUTIVES; AAUTOMOBILE INDUSTRY 
-- LABOR RELATIONS; AUTOMOBILE INDUSTRY -- UNITED STATES 
</P>
